The '''Starspin''' was a type of small [[Starship/Legends|starship]] that was manufactured by [[Kuat Drive Yards/Legends|Kuat Drive Yards]]. A ''Starspin'' was used by the [[Black Sun/Legends|Black Sun]] operative [[Mathal]] during his ill-fated trip to meet with [[Tarnese Bleyd]]. The ship was presumably [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]]-equipped, however it was relatively small in size.

